<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>FAHATSIAROVANA ASAFA36</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Mivory eto ny mpanomponao
 Hankatoa ny Didy 'zay napetrakao

[V2]
 Izao no ataoko hahatsiarovana
 'Zay nataon'ny Tompo nanavotana ahy

[V3]
 Ity no mofo toy ny tenany
 Efa noratraina ho ahy izay nania

[V4]
 'Ty no kapoaka mampahatsiahy fa
 Latsaka ny Rany nanadiovana ahy

[V5]
 Koa raiso Tompo ny fisaorako
 Mendrika ho anao 'Lay Mpamonjiko</lyrics>
<hymn_number>36</hymn_number>
<author>Groupe Mobile</author>
</song>